---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Nav from "../components/Nav.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Scope | Home Remodel RFP" description="Project scope and requirements">
  <Fragment slot="nav"><Nav /></Fragment>
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6 py-10 space-y-6">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold">Project Scope</h1>
    <section class="space-y-3">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Main House ("The Box")</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 text-slate-700">
        <li>Approximately 2,400 sq ft, 2-story.</li>
        <li>Currently mid-construction.</li>
        <li>Framing: floor joists are 2x8; wall studs are 2x6.</li>
        <li>Potential for 4 bedrooms and 2 baths downstairs. Bedrooms could be locked off to create a studio (Junior ADU) and/or a 2 BR / 2 BA lock-off Junior ADU. <span class="font-medium">Plans and permits needed.</span></li>
        <li>Upstairs is planned and permitted/approved for kitchen, living, dining, and a half bath. Desired upgrade to a full bath (shower only).</li>
        <li>Includes a previously permitted/approved woodburning stove.</li>
        <li>Downstairs: remove 3â€“5 walls to create an entry; add at least 4 new walls.</li>
        <li>Upstairs: complete framing and trim-out; install appliances.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-3">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Garage Building</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 text-slate-700">
        <li>Two-car garage.</li>
        <li>One-car garage.</li>
        <li>1 BR / 1 BA unpermitted ADU reportedly inhabited for 50+ years (documented statements available). Needs laminate flooring and a gas stove to be complete; washer and dryer hookups are inside the unit.</li>
        <li>Roof improvements completed with plans and permits. There are now two additional rooms and a loft/landing upstairs that are not trimmed out and have no plumbing. No external ingress/egress; current access via interior garage staircase and landing.</li>
        <li><span class="font-medium">Note:</span> Owner has plans for this building; appears process to legalize additional living space was started, but to current knowledge, no plans were submitted for approval.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </section>
  <Fragment slot="footer"><Footer /></Fragment>
</BaseLayout>
